1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:48,960
[Story of Yanxi Palace]
[Episode 38]

3
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:53,120
Continue with her treatment.
Tell her to recuperate in peace.

4
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,200
Young Master!

5
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,780
Young Master!

6
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,640
Why is this perfume pouch with you?

7
00:02:07,070 --> 00:02:09,229
When I was making your bed,

8
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,420
I accidentally picked up this pouch.

9
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:15,280
Young Mistress must have misunderstood it.
That's why she was so furious.

10
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:18,340
After that, when she was
not paying attention, I hid it.

11
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:22,860
When she hit you just now,
why didn't you just hand it to her?

12
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:25,180
You hid it under your pillow so carefully.

13
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:26,640
You must treasure it a lot.

14
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,160
Thank you.

15
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,680
Young Master!

16
00:02:36,260 --> 00:02:37,590
You are injured. Get up.

17
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:40,840
I know that I've caused you trouble,

18
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:45,120
but can you please have mercy on me
and not sell me?

19
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:50,930
[Young Master.]

20
00:02:53,250 --> 00:02:54,320
Butler Liu.

21
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,940
Yes, Young Master.

22
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:59,630
After Qing Lian recovers,
let her continue to clean my study room.

23
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:00,890
As for Young Mistress,

24
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:04,930
-she's banned from entering my study room.
-Yes, Young Master.

25
00:03:35,610 --> 00:03:38,600
You always work until so late.
It's bad for your health.

26
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,450
I cooked this ginseng soup for you.

27
00:03:40,450 --> 00:03:42,050
Drink it before it gets cold.

28
00:03:48,090 --> 00:03:49,130
Fu Heng,

29
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:52,720
I didn't know that the hairpin was for me.

30
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:54,579
That's why I acted like that.

31
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:58,750
Look.

32
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,660
I already asked a craftsman to fix it.

33
00:04:02,830 --> 00:04:03,950
Take a look at it.

34
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,280
Fu Heng, I was wrong.

35
00:04:11,390 --> 00:04:13,450
Can you please stop being angry at me?

36
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,720
Er Qing,

37
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:18,120
do you know what your mistake is?

38
00:04:19,850 --> 00:04:22,890
We've just been recently married.

39
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,070
You are always busy
with official affairs...

40
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:28,380
and have no time
to care about my feelings.

41
00:04:28,380 --> 00:04:29,840
I treated her like that...

42
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:32,700
because I was too jealous
to think straight.

43
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,700
It's not a big deal.

44
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:38,920
If you like her,
you can take her as your concubine.

45
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:41,250
But she comes from a lowly family.

46
00:04:41,290 --> 00:04:42,940
She'll embarrass you.

47
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:47,240
Why can't you understand yet?

48
00:04:47,990 --> 00:04:49,630
I've already apologized.

49
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:52,060
Why are you still being so harsh?

50
00:04:52,060 --> 00:04:53,900
Just because of a misunderstanding,

51
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:55,540
you cut her hair...

52
00:04:55,830 --> 00:04:57,630
and pulled out her fingernails.

53
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,990
She's also a person.

54
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,980
Is human life so worthless in your eyes?

55
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:05,010
Why are you so concerned about her?

56
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:12,760
The Er Qing who I saw
in Changchun Palace in the past...

57
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:15,920
was gentle, virtuous, refined and amiable.

58
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,400
But now,

59
00:05:19,010 --> 00:05:21,270
you're always focusing on socialising.

60
00:05:22,110 --> 00:05:25,400
You exchange all news about
Fuca's mansion with Laiboo.

61
00:05:26,150 --> 00:05:28,040
And you even bullied a maidservant.

62
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:30,440
Are you really here
to lead a peaceful life?

63
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:34,470
The Laiboo you mentioned is
my grandfather. He's not an outsider!

64
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:39,080
Shouldn't the officials stick together?
Don't you need his support?

65
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:40,320
I don't need it!

66
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,640
His Majesty hates it the most
when the officials form a party.

67
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:46,880
I've already warned you many times.
Why do you remain incorrigible?

68
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,440
You sound so righteous.

69
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:53,600
But I think you are so fussy because
you are still in love with Wei Ying Luo!

70
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,700
That's why I'm such an eyesore to you!

71
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,530
Yes.

72
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:06,200
I admit that she's still in my mind.

73
00:06:08,050 --> 00:06:09,410
But I'm trying.

74
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:11,990
I'm trying to treat you better.

75
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,780
I try to give you everything you want.

76
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,350
But now,

77
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:21,220
every time I see you,
you'll remind me of that bloody hands.

78
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,770
Let me tell you this.

79
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,480
Wei Ying Luo is more vicious than I am!

80
00:06:27,580 --> 00:06:31,150
She knows whom to love and whom to hate.
She'll never hurt an innocent!

81
00:06:31,150 --> 00:06:32,270
But what about you?

82
00:06:33,380 --> 00:06:36,840
You destroyed the life of someone
out of a moment of jealously!

83
00:06:37,850 --> 00:06:40,450
It doesn't matter even
if you can't forget her.

84
00:06:40,790 --> 00:06:42,830
I'm your wife now.

85
00:06:42,930 --> 00:06:44,930
I'm the person that you should love.

86
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,600
Hitara Er Qing.

87
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,440
In my eyes,

88
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,860
you can never be compared to Wei Ying Luo.

89
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,380
And I'm disgusted...

90
00:06:56,020 --> 00:06:58,420
with your maliciousness and viciousness.

91
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,240
Fu Heng.

92
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,840
Fu Heng!

93
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,670
Fu Heng!

94
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,520
Fu Heng!

95
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:14,960
Fu Heng.

96
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,680
Come back.

97
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,280
Come back!

98
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:22,160
Get up. The ground is cold.

99
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:25,000
What have I done wrong?

100
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,730
What have I done wrong?

101
00:07:29,850 --> 00:07:33,580
I asked my grandfather to support him,
but he didn't appreciate it.

102
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:37,330
I socialised with the wives
of those in power.

103
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:40,420
And he accused me for
bandying information around.

104
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:43,590
And he blamed me for
punishing a maidservant.

105
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:46,740
Everything I did was for him.

106
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:51,430
But he hates me so much.

107
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,440
Can you tell me why?

108
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,600
Can anyone tell me why?

109
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,240
[Fuca Fu Heng,]

110
00:08:17,490 --> 00:08:19,340
[this is too much.]

111
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,100
[One day,]

112
00:08:23,730 --> 00:08:27,290
[I will let you know
how much pain I'm in now.]

113
00:08:35,850 --> 00:08:36,690
Zhen Zhu,

114
00:08:40,190 --> 00:08:41,590
deliver this to the room.

115
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,600
Alright.

116
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:47,200
What's wrong?

117
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,200
Er Qing is here again.

118
00:08:49,290 --> 00:08:50,930
She keeps on crying.

119
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,040
Don't get into her way.

120
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:57,880
Weren't you best friends in the past?

121
00:08:58,580 --> 00:08:59,740
What happened?

122
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:04,790
Ever since she became the Young Mistress
of Fuca mansion, she changed.

123
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:07,700
She is now resplendent with jewels
and is insufferably arrogant.

124
00:09:07,700 --> 00:09:09,220
I'm just a servant.

125
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:11,520
I'm not worthy enough to be her friend.

126
00:09:13,170 --> 00:09:15,050
People won't change that fast.

127
00:09:16,140 --> 00:09:17,600
If she has really changed,

128
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,960
it just means that
you didn't notice it before.

129
00:09:21,850 --> 00:09:23,220
You are right.

130
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:27,930
Her Majesty used to say that she's very
calculative. Looks like she was right.

131
00:09:27,930 --> 00:09:30,560
Er Qing has always been unwilling
to be a palace maid.

132
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:34,040
Now, she's just exposing her true nature.

133
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:38,060
You are still so young.
Why are you sighing all day long?

134
00:09:38,190 --> 00:09:40,350
You'll grow old faster because of it.

135
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:43,360
What are you doing?

136
00:09:44,590 --> 00:09:45,760
What are these?

137
00:09:46,330 --> 00:09:47,390
Sister Ming Yu,

138
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:50,150
these are Young Mistress Fuca's luggage.

139
00:09:56,770 --> 00:09:59,300
My goodness! Is she
moving back to the palace?

140
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,600
This is outrageous.

141
00:10:06,100 --> 00:10:07,190
Your Majesty,

142
00:10:08,010 --> 00:10:11,130
I had served you for six years.
I'm used to it already.

143
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,650
Although I've left the palace,

144
00:10:15,170 --> 00:10:17,480
I still miss you very much.

145
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:21,120
In the past, palace maids
who served Empress Dowager...

146
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,240
would be summoned back to serve her...

147
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:25,840
even after they were married
because they missed her.

148
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,770
I'm now married into Fuca mansion.

149
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,360
I'm your sister-in-law.

150
00:10:29,940 --> 00:10:32,470
What's wrong with me
coming back to serve you?

151
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:35,640
But I already have Ying Luo
and Ming Yu to serve me.

152
00:10:36,790 --> 00:10:39,320
-I don't need you to come back.
-Your Majesty.

153
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:44,800
Fu Heng is always been busy
with his official work.

154
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,200
He only comes back...

155
00:10:47,350 --> 00:10:48,950
two or three times in a month.

156
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:52,000
And he always stays alone
in his study room.

157
00:10:52,350 --> 00:10:53,590
I am...

158
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,820
too lonely and miserable at home.

159
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:59,580
That's why I want to
come back to accompany you.

160
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,700
Your Majesty,

161
00:11:03,970 --> 00:11:05,930
don't you want me either?

162
00:11:10,290 --> 00:11:11,330
Er Qing,

163
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,320
tell me the truth.

164
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,200
What happened?

165
00:11:29,530 --> 00:11:31,510
Fu Heng favours a maidservant...

166
00:11:31,770 --> 00:11:33,430
and often quarrels with me.

167
00:11:34,490 --> 00:11:35,850
Due to anger,

168
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,000
I punished that maidservant...

169
00:11:38,410 --> 00:11:39,940
and sent Fu Heng into a rage.

170
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,620
Based on my understanding of him,

171
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:47,920
Fu Heng has never been so furious before.

172
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,400
That implies that...

173
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,850
you've made a grave mistake...

174
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,450
-this time.
-Your Majesty.

175
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,010
Please allow me to...

176
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,170
accompany you here for a while.

177
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:01,640
At least...

178
00:12:02,710 --> 00:12:04,960
At least wait until Fu Heng's rage
has died down...

179
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,960
before asking me to go back, okay?

180
00:12:10,810 --> 00:12:11,980
Fine.

181
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:15,120
You can stay here for the moment then.

182
00:12:17,980 --> 00:12:19,380
Thank you, Your Majesty.

183
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:32,820
Mistress, what do you need?

184
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:37,220
My luggage has not been unpacked yet.

185
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,640
Go and unpack it for me.

186
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,120
Her Majesty's legs...

187
00:12:42,450 --> 00:12:45,000
are always in pain during rainy days.

188
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:47,820
I have to give her a massage right now.

189
00:12:47,850 --> 00:12:49,490
Ming Yu will do it.

190
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,070
As for you,

191
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:54,100
you just need to unpack my luggage for me.

192
00:12:54,250 --> 00:12:58,180
I'll ask someone else to help you
with it then. Please wait for a moment.

193
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,530
Wei Ying Luo!

194
00:12:59,970 --> 00:13:01,330
How dare you!

195
00:13:01,740 --> 00:13:03,670
How dare you go against my command?

196
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:10,040
This area under your feet

197
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:12,640
is Forbidden City.

198
00:13:13,830 --> 00:13:15,290
This is Changchun Palace.

199
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:17,160
Not Fuca mansion.

200
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:18,360
Here,

201
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,840
Her Majesty's needs come first.

202
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:25,100
I'm the mistress and you are the servant!

203
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:27,410
I'm going to teach you today...

204
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:31,000
about rules and decorum!

205
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:35,820
Are you crazy? How dare you hit me.

206
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:38,970
If you want to act like a tyrant,
go back to Fuca mansion!

207
00:13:39,020 --> 00:13:42,400
This is Forbidden City. Everyone here
is the servant of His Majesty!

208
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,840
Your status...

209
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,190
is just the same as ours.

210
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:47,860
If I did a mistake,

211
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:50,030
Her Majesty will punish me.

212
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:53,730
How dare you act on
Her Majesty's behalf here?

213
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:54,960
Servants.

214
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:56,480
Servants!

215
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:57,990
Servants!

216
00:13:59,780 --> 00:14:00,790
Servants!

217
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:03,770
-Zhen Zhu!
-Hitara Er Qing.

218
00:14:06,140 --> 00:14:07,550
Changchun Palace...

219
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:10,640
is no longer your territory.

220
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:14,440
You better don't behave atrociously here.

221
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:19,380
Aren't you afraid that...

222
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:22,400
I'll tell Her Majesty about this?

223
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:26,320
When Her Majesty needed you the most,

224
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:32,360
you got married and left the palace
without any hesitation.

225
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:34,140
You never even looked back.

226
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:37,000
Now, think about it.

227
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:41,040
Who will Her Majesty believe?

228
00:14:50,160 --> 00:14:52,090
Hu Po, Zhen Zhu,

229
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:54,140
the corridor is too slippery.

230
00:14:55,640 --> 00:14:58,240
Mistress Fuca accidentally
slipped and fell.

231
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:00,810
Please assist her back to her room.

232
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:09,900
-Mistress Fuca…
-Don't touch me!

233
00:15:31,130 --> 00:15:32,380
Sister Er Qing.

234
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,110
Don't call me that!

235
00:15:37,780 --> 00:15:39,600
How did I treat you before this?

236
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:44,360
Now, all of you are
bought over by Wei Ying Luo.

237
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:47,570
You just ignored me, how ungrateful.

238
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:48,890
Sister Er Qing.

239
00:15:51,310 --> 00:15:53,040
The whole Changchun Palace...

240
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:55,090
is now under Wei Ying Luo's control.

241
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:58,240
Now, even Sister Ming Yu sides her.

242
00:15:58,570 --> 00:16:01,400
It won't do you any good
to go against her.

243
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:06,290
Her Majesty...

244
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:09,500
Her Majesty really trusts her that much?

245
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:11,120
Wei Ying Luo is very loyal...

246
00:16:11,460 --> 00:16:13,260
to Her Majesty.

247
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:15,840
During the days when Her Majesty was sick,

248
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:18,150
many were trying to
snoop around or do evil things.

249
00:16:18,150 --> 00:16:19,720
This place was in a chaos.

250
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:22,840
She flatly refused all visitors and
tightly closed the palace gates.

251
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,680
She only focused on
Her Majesty's recovery.

252
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:27,720
And she remained by Her Majesty's
side at all times to take care of her.

253
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:30,650
Not only Her Majesty,
even other people...

254
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:32,820
sincerely admired her because of it.

255
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,230
So,

256
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:40,000
don't pick a fight with her.
Try to stay away from her.

257
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:41,680
Alright.

258
00:16:43,690 --> 00:16:44,990
Thank you, Hu Po.

259
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:49,920
I will never forget
how well you treated me...

260
00:16:49,990 --> 00:16:51,830
when I just entered the palace.

261
00:16:52,260 --> 00:16:53,790
I'll always be on your side.

262
00:16:56,420 --> 00:16:58,200
If there's anything
I need in the future...

263
00:16:58,200 --> 00:17:00,060
Just give me the instructions...

264
00:17:00,180 --> 00:17:01,740
and I'll do my best.

265
