sew a bellyband for the little prince.

537
00:33:50,800 --> 00:33:53,350
You're really not angry at me anymore?

538
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:58,800
I promise that I won't hide
anything from you again, okay?

539
00:33:59,610 --> 00:34:01,350
Stop being angry at me.

540
00:34:01,520 --> 00:34:03,330
Stop being angry at me.

541
00:34:04,060 --> 00:34:07,550
Go and accompany Her Majesty.
Make sure that she doesn't fall down.

542
00:34:07,550 --> 00:34:09,000
Er Qing is already with her.

543
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,159
Go with them.

544
00:34:12,600 --> 00:34:14,460
Fine. I'll go with them now.

545
00:34:14,639 --> 00:34:16,840
I don't know why you are
so suspicious of her.

546
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:18,900
Why are you still
so paranoid after so long?

547
00:34:18,900 --> 00:34:20,020
Go now.

548
00:34:29,120 --> 00:34:30,330
Here you go.

549
00:34:33,340 --> 00:34:35,600
Yong Rong has become
so close to you now.

550
00:34:35,850 --> 00:34:39,510
He will start looking for you
every time he wakes up in the morning.

551
00:34:49,440 --> 00:34:50,760
Okay now. Let's go.

552
00:34:55,239 --> 00:34:56,370
Your Majesty,

553
00:34:57,080 --> 00:34:58,680
I've already deciphered...

554
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:01,070
the chess game you left for me yesterday.

555
00:35:01,070 --> 00:35:02,260
Do you want to see it?

556
00:35:02,520 --> 00:35:05,180
I suddenly remember that
I have something to do.

557
00:35:05,540 --> 00:35:07,000
You should go to bed first.

558
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,390
Your Majesty.

559
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:13,690
Farewell, Your Majesty.

560
00:35:18,120 --> 00:35:20,720
Your Highness,
what's wrong with His Majesty?

561
00:35:20,860 --> 00:35:22,740
He looks so troubled.

562
00:35:26,680 --> 00:35:28,040
What day is it today?

563
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:44,980
Your Majesty, drinking too much wine
will harm your health.

564
00:35:44,980 --> 00:35:47,970
-Let me replace it with a cup of warm tea.
-Go away.

565
00:35:56,470 --> 00:35:57,470
Your Majesty,

566
00:35:58,360 --> 00:36:01,560
if you are troubled by something,
please tell us about it.

567
00:36:01,670 --> 00:36:03,830
Although I'm dumb,

568
00:36:04,460 --> 00:36:07,330
I might be able to relieve
some of your worries.

569
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:10,510
Today...

570
00:36:11,180 --> 00:36:13,310
is the death anniversary of Yong Lian.

571
00:36:27,120 --> 00:36:29,710
When my father named him Yong Lian,

572
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:34,860
he had the intention of
letting him succeed the throne.

573
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:40,760
Yong Lian didn't disappoint him as well.

574
00:36:41,420 --> 00:36:44,350
He was naturally intelligent
and was very diligent.

575
00:36:48,430 --> 00:36:49,680
When he was eight,

576
00:36:50,740 --> 00:36:53,000
I brought him along for an imperial hunt.

577
00:36:54,080 --> 00:36:56,040
He shot down an eagle...

578
00:36:57,680 --> 00:36:59,490
and personally brought it to me.

579
00:37:00,560 --> 00:37:02,160
Among all the princes,

580
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:05,480
Yong Lian was my favourite son.

581
00:37:13,360 --> 00:37:14,460
Unfortunately,

582
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:17,640
his lifespan was short.

583
00:37:18,720 --> 00:37:20,110
He died young.

584
00:37:22,560 --> 00:37:24,420
When I saw the sixth prince today,

585
00:37:26,120 --> 00:37:28,050
I couldn't help but to think of him.

586
00:37:32,800 --> 00:37:33,900
Your Majesty,

587
00:37:34,370 --> 00:37:36,570
when Crown Prince Duanhui passed away,

588
00:37:37,550 --> 00:37:40,880
you called off all court meetings
for five days to mourn him.

589
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:43,940
You're are a very loving father.

590
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:01,760
How could there be
a father in this world...

591
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:05,600
who never shed tears when his son died?

592
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:14,240
But an emperor can only cry...

593
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:16,760
for three reasons.

594
00:38:19,720 --> 00:38:21,980
The first is for the death of his parents.

595
00:38:22,560 --> 00:38:25,200
The second is when a serious
natural disaster befalls us.

596
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:27,330
And the third is when the empire falls.

597
00:38:28,510 --> 00:38:29,660
Otherwise,

598
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:32,820
he will be punished by heaven
and his ancestors.

599
00:38:34,340 --> 00:38:35,580
I'm the son of heaven.

600
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:40,850
All the citizens in this empire
are my children.

601
00:38:42,300 --> 00:38:44,100
Yong Lian is not my only son.

602
00:38:45,200 --> 00:38:46,280
So,

603
00:38:47,780 --> 00:38:50,640
even if Her Majesty hated me
for being heartless...

604
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,120
and cold,

605
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:56,420
I had never shed a tear...

606
00:38:57,040 --> 00:38:58,360
or showed my pain.

607
00:39:03,520 --> 00:39:04,720
But tonight,

608
00:39:09,270 --> 00:39:10,310
I...

609
00:39:14,060 --> 00:39:15,790
keep thinking about Yong Lian.

610
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,670
Your Majesty,

611
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:25,010
I am not a smooth talker.

612
00:39:25,600 --> 00:39:28,080
I don't know how to comfort you.

613
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,600
But I think that...

614
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:33,850
since Her Majesty is pregnant now,

615
00:39:34,520 --> 00:39:36,080
the future little prince...

616
00:39:36,080 --> 00:39:39,280
will surely be as smart as
Crown Prince Duanhui back then.

617
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:42,000
He won't disappoint you.

618
00:39:49,360 --> 00:39:50,490
Your Majesty!

619
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:54,600
Your Majesty!

620
00:39:57,640 --> 00:39:59,370
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty,

621
00:39:59,500 --> 00:40:01,300
Her Majesty has just gone to bed.

622
00:40:01,490 --> 00:40:03,090
What's wrong, Your Majesty?

623
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:16,130
You are that...

624
00:40:17,200 --> 00:40:18,760
annoying Wei Ying Luo.

625
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:23,430
Why will you appear even in my dream?

626
00:40:27,390 --> 00:40:28,460
You are annoying.

627
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:30,650
You are so annoying.

628
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:46,320
Look at you.

629
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:49,620
You are a little bit pretty.

630
00:40:50,160 --> 00:40:51,840
But you are so cunning.

631
00:40:52,200 --> 00:40:53,830
Woman who looks like you...

632
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:56,920
is destined to be alone forever.

633
00:40:58,040 --> 00:41:00,100
You'll stay in the palace forever...

634
00:41:00,300 --> 00:41:02,300
and I have to feed you for a lifetime.

635
00:41:05,960 --> 00:41:06,970
Your Majesty!

636
00:41:08,480 --> 00:41:09,740
What's wrong?

637
00:41:10,020 --> 00:41:11,120
Your Majesty.

638
00:41:14,340 --> 00:41:15,860
Why did you drink so much?

639
00:41:17,520 --> 00:41:20,320
The imperial physician
checked your pulse today.

640
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:23,760
This baby will surely be a prince.

641
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:26,000
I know that...

642
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:29,200
Yong Lian is coming back to us.

643
00:41:30,150 --> 00:41:31,180
Your Majesty,

644
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:34,680
-what are you talking about?
-Yong Lian...

645
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:39,640
was intelligent and good-looking.
There was no one like him.

646
00:41:41,110 --> 00:41:43,830
He'll always be my most beloved son.

647
00:41:44,520 --> 00:41:45,760
When he passed away,

648
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:48,360
I was so sad.

649
00:41:49,520 --> 00:41:50,920
My heart ached.

650
00:41:53,450 --> 00:41:54,810
But I knew that...

651
00:41:55,710 --> 00:41:58,560
one day, he will surely come back to us.

652
00:42:00,910 --> 00:42:01,910
Look.

653
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,720
He'll come back to us soon.

654
00:42:11,630 --> 00:42:13,170
What are you looking at?

655
00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:14,450
Li Yu.

656
00:42:15,430 --> 00:42:18,510
She always angers me.
I hate her so much.

657
00:42:18,600 --> 00:42:19,770
She's so spiteful!

658
00:42:19,810 --> 00:42:22,120
-Your Majesty, calm down!
-She's indeed spiteful!

659
00:42:22,120 --> 00:42:23,320
-Your Majesty.
-Ying Luo.

660
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:24,320
Let me tell you...

661
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:26,350
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

662
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:27,940
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

663
00:42:27,940 --> 00:42:28,940
Your Majesty.

664
00:42:29,270 --> 00:42:30,400
Forgive me.

665
00:42:30,640 --> 00:42:31,810
I'm fine.

666
00:42:34,220 --> 00:42:35,210
Your Majesty,

667
00:42:35,770 --> 00:42:37,410
be careful of your health.

668
00:42:39,720 --> 00:42:41,150
Ask Yong Lian this.

669
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:44,680
I was always busy...

670
00:42:45,600 --> 00:42:47,400
with state affairs before this.

671
00:42:47,590 --> 00:42:49,330
I never accompanied him even for a day.

672
00:42:49,330 --> 00:42:50,770
I never even hugged him.

673
00:42:52,630 --> 00:42:54,070
Does he blame me?

674
00:42:54,830 --> 00:42:56,230
Is he willing...

675
00:43:00,740 --> 00:43:02,310
to be my son again?
